The lot is designated horse property and provides ample space for a custom homesite and related improvements. Elevated topography offers privacy and scenic surroundings while remaining conveniently located-approximately five minutes from Saguaro National Monument East and less than ten minutes from Houghton Northwest Hospital, shopping, dining, and entertainment. Buyer to verify zoning, utilities, access, and development feasibility. Ideal for those seeking space, views, and a blank canvas to create a custom vision.
